Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.50,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(恐怖的畢克．薩姆！)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我所做的事\N竟同時一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機，史中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左右引擊，受損了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉，聽到嗎？\N回答吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了，在第三甲板降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事？少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.61,0:02:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右方的導彈很薄弱\N不要大意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞‧波\N交由副艦長來做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.49,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖戰鬥中是禁止私人交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但很見外呀！米萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是去保護妳\N我也是可做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.81,0:03:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白妳的感受\N在等妳呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊有點不適\N去代她一會吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來代替了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對空機關鎗\N左方快接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點！快點修好左右引擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏威多！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我修好被損的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有加大二號引擊的輸出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加大點吧！\NOK，會做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.04,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有燃料和彈藥的補給\N快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等15分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10分鐘\N我也去補給燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點吧！\N用10分鐘去完成吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏威多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了待機室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，沒受傷的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉，來這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少尉，停止吧！\N很難為情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉，出發準備完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜呢！         中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.96,0:05:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊少尉\N雖人在年青時會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同的事\N但現在自己的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太過認真比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了吧！         中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是能接受\N少尉的愛的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於我來說\N少尉太耀眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不同的世界   但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是便宜的東西\N媽媽的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如失去就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我好好保管吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.94,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那戒指拜託了，少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球背後\N南方的300公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是基斯比加基地\N古蘭拿達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.18,0:06:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所羅門要出擊的軍隊\N不斷在準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在馬古比司令的麾下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,編成了一支艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在基地之內\N留下很多的戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意吧！\N是新型的敵人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？有多少台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，好像\N只得一台新型敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餘下只有多姆和薩克\N去攻吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！對方的作戰能力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了呀！蠢材們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他們看這畢克．薩姆和普通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS不同之處吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如出來的話\N就快點出來呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射槍竟然...\N怪...怪物呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物？去查個明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是基斯，閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？\N閣下在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在操控著畢克．薩姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對抗侵入的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，殘餘的艦隊\N也出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用閣下親自出擊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.67,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.87,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用全部的戰力\N去攻擊不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茜拿，美利巴\N無事的逃出了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我軍的逃生火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.97,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路程是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是從\N所羅門發射出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩護的回收吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泰沙，所羅門的戰鬥\N好像是嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用管那逃生火箭...\N失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.22,0:10:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請馬古比殿下\N你明白兵士的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我！         這樣的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要相信的去救出同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.56,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵士也一樣\N和我們在宇宙中戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點的話\N會離開回收範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.80,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，回收吧！      係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美利巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是同伴的艦隊呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖這傢伙強大火力是好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不可再使基地受到損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基斯！         係，閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦艇還餘下多少台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了敵方的新兵器和MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四分之三被破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餘下是不能開動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！去突破\N敵方的中央艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.18,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也用餘下的多姆和薩克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開所羅門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閣下也請努力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在後方，確認敵艦在移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可忍耐吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在所羅門餘下的敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用反射鏡系統\N能消滅他們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如有60%\N的準確率的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去試試看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,定向坐標是0635
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入Y射線\N004，002
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在發射太陽能系統後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各艦隊去消滅敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入最大速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯過去也可以\N還有在前方前來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一隻也要擊下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這邊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很拿手吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.51,0:13:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟是什麼MS\N造成這樣的破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所羅門還在出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射鏡在瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.83,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？反射鏡還在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餘下的艦隻\N去襲擊敵方艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！         畢克．薩姆的目標是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準後方的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要理會小卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉中了彈\N在第三甲板回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各部門\N去追著所羅門出發的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大型MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊！   對不起中尉\N已沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！巴馬士，回到副橋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉向180度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點，米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵艦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊\N用全部雷射光射去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.79,0:15:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然，不只是大型的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，的確彈回了雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是用導彈才有效嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去，只有增加損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢克．薩姆單獨去敵方艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.61,0:16:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N發出逃走的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用了太多的戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖很遺憾\N但只有放棄所羅門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那操控系統\N移到我這處吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也各自逃走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，閣下！\N不要白白犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有多姆和薩克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如用那的話\N能從戰場中逃去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！發出起航信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢克．薩姆由我來操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.65,0:16:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣，所羅門\N會簡單的擊下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣做很困難的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這畢克．薩姆是不怕雷射光攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我帶你們\N到地獄下去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的MS\N在發射強力的磁場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是導彈，用導彈來迎擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓倒性的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到嗎？\N如畢克．薩姆能量產生後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能一瞬間的\N打敗聯邦軍呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.00,0:18:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相接後，用G裝甲來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真慢，阿姆羅少曹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是中尉，是打算怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有什麼打算嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要破壞磁場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有接近去用雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如這邊的雷射光用完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用鋼彈的雷射槍和雷射劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如用盡所有武器\N我會被打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私情是禁忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可再更加的受損傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.97,0:18:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖很悲傷\N但這是戰爭呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！從下方去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下方嗎？對空型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟被一台MS...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這畢克．薩姆被打敗了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被打敗呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被你打敗呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被打敗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁的光榮，我的自尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被打敗，不會被打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會被打敗呀！\N是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.84,0:20:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所羅門...墮下了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？泰沙\N用這古亞知送邵娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去古蘭拿達吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我移到去知比\N去看清今後的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那全部終於也失敗了\N是吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你始終是堅持\N所羅門的作戰參謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還餘下情報收集\N和逃生的兵士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了\N我去執行那任務吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說謊的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.83,0:21:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能說是說謊嗎？阿姆羅

